        This is determined using a server side alogrithm based on the browser agent. 
        For more information, please see this <a class="underline" href="http://www.deanhume.com/Home/BlogPost/webp---advanced-image-optimization-using-asp-net-mvc/89">link</a>.</p>
    <hr />
    <h2>Black/White/Grey Image</h2>
    @Html.DrawImage("/Images/test.jpg", "This is a test image")
    <h2>High Colour Image</h2>
    @Html.DrawImage("/Images/shard.jpg", "Aqua Shard")
</div>
